00:50:35.870 --> 00:50:38.240
So one is the little
bet about metal prices,

00:50:38.240 --> 00:50:40.740
the second is the bet on
the Carter Reagan election,

00:50:40.740 --> 00:50:43.140
but the third bet is the
bet about the future.

00:50:43.140 --> 00:50:48.340
And so it's really a
grand historical question.

00:50:48.340 --> 00:50:52.170
So are we coming to the
end of an age, fueled

00:50:52.170 --> 00:50:54.070
