and this can't be sustained--

00:51:01.450 --> 00:51:05.270
or is this a path that we
can continue into the future?

00:51:05.270 --> 00:51:09.710
And I think that there
are interesting arguments

00:51:09.710 --> 00:51:11.540
on both sides of that
question in terms

00:51:11.540 --> 00:51:14.900
of how-- and the technology,
it's uncertain about how

00:51:14.900 --> 00:51:17.146
the technology is going to
unfold in terms pf to what

00:51:17.146 --> 00:51:19.520
extent we're going be able to
move away from fossil fuels

00:51:19.520 --> 00:51:25.990
to find sufficient other energy
sources to meet our needs.

